## Location and Venue

The event takes place at Koelnmesse in Cologne, Germany, one of the world's leading exhibition centers for the technology and entertainment industries. The venue offers state-of-the-art facilities, excellent transportation connections, and is located in the heart of Cologne, making it easily accessible by public transport, car, or plane via Cologne Bonn Airport.
